ğŸ”’ Why this happens (the truth)

In FlatLaf 3.4:

The title bar height is calculated internally

It depends on:

Font size

DPI scaling

Button insets

OS metrics


FlatLaf intentionally does NOT expose a height property
(to avoid broken window controls across platforms)


â¡ï¸ This is by design, not a bug.


